'''一氧化硫'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为SO。它只能以低浓度气体存在。当浓缩或进入凝聚相，它会二聚成[[二氧化二硫|S<sub>2</sub>O<sub>2</sub>]]。在太空已经检测到一氧化硫，但是很少有完整分子存在。

==结构和成键==
一氧化硫的基态和[[氧气|O<sub>2</sub>]]和[[二硫|S<sub>2</sub>]]相似，为三线态。也就是说，一氧化硫中有两个不成对的电子。<ref name = greenwood>{{Greenwood&Earnshaw}}</ref>其中的S−O [[键长|键长]]是148.1 pm，和其它[[低氧化硫|低氧化硫]]（例如S<sub>8</sub>O中的S−O键长为148 pm）的键长类似，但比气态[[一氧化二硫|S<sub>2</sub>O]]（146 pm）、[[二氧化硫|SO<sub>2</sub>]]（143.1 pm）和[[三氧化硫|SO<sub>3</sub>]]（142 pm）的键长长。<ref name = greenwood />

[[近红外线|近红外线]]可以将一氧化硫激发到单线态（没有不成对电子）。它的反应性比基态三线态高，就和[[单线态氧|单线态氧]]比[[三线态氧|三线态氧]]更具反应性一样。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Near-Infrared-Light-Induced Reaction of Singlet SO with Allene and Dimethylacetylene in a Rare Gas Matrix. Infrared Spectra of Two Novel Episulfoxides|last1=Salama|first1=F.|last2=Frei|first2=H. J.|journal=Journal of Physical Chemistry|date=1989|volume=93|page=1285–1292|doi=10.1021/j100341a023}}</ref>

==生产和反应==
作为有机合成试剂的一氧化硫的生产主要集中在使用可以“挤出”SO的化合物。这些化合物包括相对简单的{{le|氧化硫丙环|ethylene episulfoxide}}<ref>{{cite journal|title=Sulfur Monoxide Chemistry. The Nature of SO from Thiirane Oxide and the Mechanism of Its Reaction with Dienes|last1=Chao|first1=P.|last2=Lemal|first2=D. M.|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=95|issue=3|date=1973|page=920|doi=10.1021/ja00784a049}}</ref>或是C<sub>10</sub>H<sub>6</sub>S<sub>3</sub>O<ref>{{cite journal|doi = 10.1021/ol016678g|pmid = 11678709|title = A Novel Recyclable Sulfur Monoxide Transfer Reagent|journal = Organic Letters|volume = 3|issue = 22|pages = 3565–3568|year = 2001|last1 = Grainger|first1 = R. S.|last2 = Procopio|first2 = A.|last3 = Steed|first3 = J. W.}}</ref>的分解：

:C<sub>2</sub>H<sub>4</sub>SO  → C<sub>2</sub>H<sub>4</sub> + SO

SO分子是热力学不稳定的，会二聚成[[二氧化二硫|S<sub>2</sub>O<sub>2</sub>]]。<ref name = greenwood/>SO会和[[烯烃|烯烃]]、[[炔烃|炔烃]]和[[二烯|二烯]]加成，形成[[环硫化物|环硫化物]]，也就是有含硫三元环的化合物。<ref>{{cite journal|title=[1+2] Cycloadditions of Sulfur Monoxide (SO) to Alkenes and Alkynes and [1+4]Cycloadditions to Dienes (Polyenes). Generation and Reactions of Singlet SO?|first1=J.|last1=Nakayama|first2=Y.|last2=Tajima|last3=Piao|first3=X.-H.|first4=Y.|last4=Sugihara|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|date=2007|volume=129|issue=23|pages=7250–7251|doi=10.1021/ja072044e|pmid=17506566}}</ref>

===在极端条件下的产生===
在实验室中，一氧化硫可以通过[[二氧化硫|二氧化硫]]和硫蒸汽{{le|辉光放电|glow discharge}}而成。<ref name = greenwood />在含有一些溶解的[[惰性气体|惰性气体]]的浓[[硫酸|硫酸]]单气泡[[声致发光|声致发光]]中也检测到了一氧化硫。<ref>{{cite journal|title=The temperatures of single-bubble sonoluminescence (A)|last1=Suslick|first1=K. S.|last2=Flannigan|first2=D. J.|journal=The Journal of the Acoustical Society of America|date=2004|volume=116|issue=4|page=2540|doi=10.1121/1.4785135|bibcode=2004ASAJ..116.2540S}}</ref>

一氧化硫基于以下反应的[[化学发光|化学发光]]：<ref>{{cite journal|title=Chemical Mechanism and Efficiency of the Sulfur Chemiluminescence Detector|last1=Benner|first1=R. L.|last2=Stedman|first2=D. H.|journal=Applied Spectroscopy|volume=48|issue=7|date=1994|page=848–851|doi=10.1366/0003702944029901|bibcode=1994ApSpe..48..848B|s2cid=98849015}}</ref>
:SO + O<sub>3</sub> →  SO<sub>2</sub>* + O<sub>2</sub>
:SO<sub>2</sub>* →  SO<sub>2</sub> + [[光子|h''ν'']]
其中*指[[激发态|激发态]]。

==存在==
===作为配体===
SO[[配体|配体]]可以以多种方式键合：<ref>{{cite journal|last=Schenk|first=W. A.|title=Sulfur Oxides as Ligands in Coordination Compounds. Angewandte Chemie International Edition in English|year=1987|volume=26|pages=98–109|doi=10.1002/anie.198700981}}</ref><ref>{{cite encyclopedia|entry=Sulfur: Inorganic Chemistry|last=Woollins|first=J. D.|encyclopedia=Encyclopedia of Inorganic Chemistry|date=1995|publisher=John Wiley and Sons|isbn=0-471-93620-0}}</ref>
*角形M−O−S结构的终端配体，例如[[氟氧化钛|氟氧化钛]]的配体<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Wei |first1=R. |last2=Chen |first2=X. |last3=Gong |first3=Y. |title=End-On Oxygen-Bound Sulfur Monoxide Complex of Titanium Oxyfluoride |journal=Inorganic Chemistry |date=2019 |volume=58 |issue=17 |pages=11801–11806 |doi=10.1021/acs.inorgchem.9b01880|pmid=31441297 }}</ref>
*角形M−S−O结构的终端配体，类似角形的[[亚硝基|亚硝基]]配体
*通过硫原子和两个或三个金属中心[[桥接|桥接]]，例如Fe<sub>3</sub>(''μ''<sup>3</sup>-S)(''μ''<sup>3</sup>-SO)(CO)<sub>9</sub>
*与[[钒|钒]]、[[铌|铌]]和[[钽|钽]]的[[哈普托数|''η''<sup>2</sup>]]侧向配位（d–π相互作用）<ref>{{cite journal|title=Side-On Sulfur Monoxide Complexes of Tantalum, Niobium, and Vanadium Oxyfluorides|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|first1=R.|last1=Wei|first2=X.|last2=Chen|first3=Y. |last3=Gong|year=2019|volume= 58|issue=6|pages=3807–3814|doi=10.1021/acs.inorgchem.8b03411|pmid=30707575}}</ref>

===天体化学===
人们已经在[[木星|木星]]的卫星之一[[木卫一|木卫一]]周围的大气<ref>{{cite journal|title=Io's atmosphere: Not yet understood|last=Lellouch|first=E.|date=1996|journal=Icarus|volume=124|page=1–21|doi=10.1006/icar.1996.0186}}</ref>和[[等离子体|等离子体]][[环面|环面]]<ref>{{cite journal|title=Detection of SO in Io's Exosphere|last1=Russell|first1=C. T.|last2=Kivelson|first2=M. G.|journal=Science|date=2000|volume=287|issue=5460|pages=1998–1999|doi=10.1126/science.287.5460.1998|pmid=10720321|bibcode=2000Sci...287.1998R}}</ref>中检测到一氧化硫。它也存在于[[金星|金星]]的大气中，<ref>{{cite journal|title=International Ultraviolet Explorer observations of Venus SO<sub>2</sub> and SO|last1=Na|first1=C. Y.|last2=Esposito|first2=L. W.|last3=Skinner|first3=T. E.|journal=Journal of Geophysical Research|volume=95|date=1990|page=7485–7491|doi=10.1029/JD095iD06p07485|bibcode=1990JGR....95.7485N}}</ref>[[海尔-波普彗星|海尔-波普彗星]]中<ref>{{cite journal|title=New Molecular Species in Comet C/1995 O1 (Hale–Bopp) Observed with the Caltech S submillimeter Observatory|first1=D. C.|last1=Lis|first2=D. M.|last2=Mehringer|first3=D.|last3=Benford|first4=M.|last4=Gardner|first5=T. G.|last5=Phillips|first6=D.|last6=Bockelée-Morvan|first7=N.|last7=Biver|first8=P.|last8=Colom|first9=J.|last9=Crovisier|first10=D.|last10=Despois|first11=H.|last11=Rauer|journal=Earth, Moon, and Planets|volume=78|issue=1–3|date=1997|pages=13–20|doi=10.1023/A:1006281802554|bibcode=1997EM&P...78...13L|s2cid=51862359}}</ref>和[[星际物质|星际物质]]里。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Observations of interstellar sulfur monoxide|last1=Gottlieb|first1=C. A.|last2=Gottlieb|first2=E. W.|last3=Litvak|first3=M. M.|last4=Ball|first4=J. A.|last5=Pennfield|first5=H.|journal=Astrophysical Journal|volume=1|issue=219|date=1978|page=77–94|doi=10.1086/155757|bibcode=1978ApJ...219...77G}}</ref>

在[[木卫一|木卫一]]中，一氧化硫被认为是由[[木卫一的火山活动|火山活动]]和[[光化学|光化学]]路径生成的。主要光化学反应如下：<ref>{{cite journal|title=Photochemistry of a Volcanically Driven Atmosphere on Io: Sulfur and Oxygen Species from a Pele-Type Eruption|last1=Moses|first1=J. I.|last2=Zolotov|first2=M. Y.|last3=Fegley|first3=B.|journal=Icarus|volume=156|page=76–106|date=2002|issue=1|doi=10.1006/icar.2001.6758|bibcode=2002Icar..156...76M}}</ref>
: O  +  S<sub>2</sub>  →  S  +  SO
: SO<sub>2</sub>  → SO  +  O

一氧化硫也被发现存在于[[天鹅座NML|天鹅座NML]]。<ref name="Marvel1996">{{cite book|first=Kevin|last=Marvel|title=The Circumstellar Environment of Evolved Stars As Revealed by Studies of Circumstellar Water Masers|chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wwx1Gj5wR5QC&pg=PR182|access-date=23 August 2012|date=1996|publisher=Universal Publishers|isbn=978-1-58112-061-5|pages=182–212|chapter=NML Cygni|archive-date=2022-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220308061108/https://books.google.com/books?id=wwx1Gj5wR5QC&pg=PR182}}</ref>

===生物化学===
一氧化硫可能具有一些生物活性。从反应产物[[羰基硫|羰基硫]]和[[二氧化硫|二氧化硫]]推断，[[猪|猪]]的[[冠状动脉|冠状动脉]]中有瞬态的一氧化硫。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Identification of carbonyl sulfide and sulfur dioxide in porcine coronary artery by gas chromatography/mass spectrometry, possible relevance to EDHF|last1=Balazy|first1=M.|last2=Abu-Yousef|first2=I. A.|last3=Harpp|first3=D. N.|last4=Park|first4=J.|journal=Biochemical and Biophysical Research Communications|date=2003|volume=311|issue=3|pages=728–734|doi=10.1016/j.bbrc.2003.10.055|pmid=14623333}}</ref>

== 双阳离子 ==
[[二氧化硫|二氧化硫]] SO<sub>2</sub>在[[六甲苯|六甲苯]] C<sub>6</sub>(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>6</sub>存在下可以被[[超强酸|超强酸]][[六氟砷酸|HF·AsF<sub>5</sub>]]质子化，产生非刚性的{{le|π配合物|Pi complex}} C<sub>6</sub>(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>6</sub>SO<sup>2+</sup>。其中的SO<sup>2+</sup>阳离子可以在[[苯环|苯环]]上无障碍移动。这个双阳离子的S−O键长为142.4(2) pm。<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Malischewski|first1=Moritz|last2=Seppelt|first2=Konrad|date=2017|title=Isolation and Characterization of a Non-Rigid Hexamethylbenzene-SO<sup>2+</sup> Complex|journal=Angewandte Chemie International Edition|language=en|volume=56|issue=52|pages=16495–16497|doi=10.1002/anie.201708552|pmid=29084371|issn=1433-7851|url=https://hal.sorbonne-universite.fr/hal-01730776/file/so_angew_sans%20marque.pdf|access-date=2021-12-26|archive-date=2021-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211226084440/https://hal.sorbonne-universite.fr/hal-01730776/file/so_angew_sans%20marque.pdf}}</ref>

: C<sub>6</sub>(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>6</sub> + SO<sub>2</sub> + 3 HF·AsF<sub>5</sub> → [C<sub>6</sub>(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>6</sub>SO][AsF<sub>6</sub>]<sub>2</sub> + [H<sub>3</sub>O][AsF<sub>6</sub>]

